Over the next few days we will be moving the builder for new Bioconductor submissions to use Bioc 3.21.  During that time the on-demand build feature may be intermittently unavailable. We appreciate your understanding.


Also of note:  for those of you with packages with "awaiting moderation" . We apologize for the delay.  We had an extremely large number of last minute submissions prior to the 3.20 release.  Any package that was submitted after the posted deadline has not yet been moderated, as we temporarily paused moderations for the organization and balance of our small review team.  Once the builders have moved to 3.21 we will begin with moderations again.

That being said:   If anyone would like to join the review team. We could greatly use more Bioconductor package reviewers.  See the following for overview, expectations, and form for sign up:  https://contributions.bioconductor.org/reviewer-resources-overview.html



